{"tid":2159141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"舉債辦校 假山瀑布仿唐建築  陝西脫貧縣8億建中學","createTime":"2020-08-16T06:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T12:35:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6df22450a3a3da7b4795186f4ec63f3fa94940ba","tid":2159141,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200815/ZM4XCKW3L5B67AVW7KJM44HYWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200815%2FZM4XCKW3L5B67AVW7KJM44HYWA%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJHqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=a34c68b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200815%2FZM4XCKW3L5B67AVW7KJM44HYWA%2F&h=ba4802b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200815/ZM4XCKW3L5B67AVW7KJM44HYWA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n舉債辦校 假山瀑布仿唐建築 <br />\n陝西脫貧縣8億建中學<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/P2jTV7w7Z4OU0tOap0yBrmnQ0jM=/2216x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M3CNJUPADBBZPLHDLFG76MSABY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FP2jTV7w7Z4OU0tOap0yBrmnQ0jM%3D%2F2216x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM3CNJUPADBBZPLHDLFG76MSABY.jpg&h=1f86ef25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新鎮安中學有24棟主建築，亦配備標準運動場，極其豪華。<br />\n<br />\n四層噴泉的「鯉躍龍門」水景、假山瀑布群、仿唐式建築，這不是中國5A級景點，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：縣官借錢拼政績 留爛攤子<br />\n<br />\n新鎮安中學項目位於陝西鎮安縣，學校佔地272畝，總建築面積12.9萬平方米，計劃容納6,000名學生，近期交付使用。新華社記者親訪現場，發現中學非常豪華，共有教學樓、宿舍樓、餐飲樓、體育館、教師公寓等主體建築24棟，設置120個班房。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用盡首五月稅收還債<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vqs7h2--iok5CtyYJObQQ54KWfQ=/1332x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XZ5LB6GGGRCJLCF7COX4BGG5NQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fvqs7h2--iok5CtyYJObQQ54KWfQ%3D%2F1332x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXZ5LB6GGGRCJLCF7COX4BGG5NQ.jpg&h=0f8da022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■校內花園小橋流水。<br />\n<br />\n記者稱：「校園內比較顯眼的是一些與教學無關的設施：從氣派的仿古牌坊式大門進入校園，四層噴泉水景沿步道拾級而上，16尊石刻鯉魚分佈兩側，一方約8米長、1.5米高的校訓大理石碑位於噴泉盡頭。據學校工作人員介紹，該水景取鯉魚跳龍門之意，從西安拉來的校訓石碑就花費了五、六萬元，單是假山瀑布水景花費超過200萬元（約223萬港元）。」<br />\n<br />\n至於在行政大樓，副書記辦公室及課管處主任辦公室同樣目測面積超過30平方米（約300呎），學校餐廳則有四層，官媒形容：「紅木鋪地、座椅扎花、餐具考究。」。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n鎮安縣委幹部透露，鎮安縣需連續12年、每年至少償還5,000多萬元貸款，強調「再窮不能窮教育」。新華社揭發，鎮安縣去年5月才脫離深度貧困縣，全年收入僅1.78億元，今年首五個月稅收只有6,081萬元（約6,787萬港元），較上年同期下降7.2%。換言之，每年單是還債已幾乎用盡該縣首五個月的稅收。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官媒斥形式主義<br />\n<br />\n新華社引述專家指，舉債辦校實際上很多資金並沒真正用在改善教學上，造成資金浪費，淪為形式主義，是一種歪曲的政績觀。另外亦有部份教師反映，校方只改善硬件，師資並沒有明顯提升，規劃亦不合理，造成了資源浪費。<br />\n<br />\n新華社"},{"pid":"a456bd5c6f7cada57eb23ea0e091e64f806486b3","tid":2159141,"uid":58247,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:52:51.000Z","msg":"支那人係鐘意做依啲門面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de5609e59e306d04f3b79f659f42a3c8dddfce1","tid":2159141,"uid":25525,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:57:06.000Z","msg":"越浮誇越難計成本，濕得越多"},{"pid":"3615fa72d3fad7f260500e228c1a316bb6079100","tid":2159141,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"以中共個格肯起學校都算係咁，好過起無人住的樓"},{"pid":"66e90b2372040638e2d9ec0acdb134a866dbbf22","tid":2159141,"uid":17859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3615fa72d3fad7f260500e228c1a316bb6079100","tid":2159141,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"以中共個格肯起學校都算係咁，好過起無人住的樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:08:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/video/沒有水的湖景-長沙樓盤現-塑膠湖-業主-侮辱智商-080700716.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https